### List all resources
GET http://localhost:3000/api/resources

### Create video resource
POST http://localhost:3000/api/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": "{TOPIC_ID}",
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W6NZfCO5SIk",
  "description": "JavaScript Tutorial for Beginners",
  "type": "video"
}

### Create article resource
POST http://localhost:3000/api/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": "{TOPIC_ID}",
  "url": "https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript",
  "description": "MDN JavaScript Documentation",
  "type": "article"
}

### Create PDF resource
POST http://localhost:3000/api/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": "{TOPIC_ID}",
  "url": "https://eloquentjavascript.net/Eloquent_JavaScript.pdf",
  "description": "Eloquent JavaScript Book PDF",
  "type": "pdf"
}

### Get resource by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/resources/{RESOURCE_ID}

### Update resource
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/resources/{RESOURCE_ID}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated: JavaScript Tutorial for Beginners - Complete Course",
  "type": "video"
}

### Delete resource
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/resources/{RESOURCE_ID}

### Get resources by topic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/resources/topic/{TOPIC_ID}

### Get resources by type - videos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/resources/type/video

### Get resources by type - articles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/resources/type/article

